      • testTableFunctionWithConfigAndSchema

        public void testTableFunctionWithConfigAndSchema()
                                          throws Exception
        Test that a schema can be provided in a table function that also includes plugin config. This case fails for the log format plugin because, unfortunately, the log format plugin has a config field called "schema" which is not a string and is found by the code before trying to treat "schema" as a schema. So, this test is disabled.
        Throws:
        Exception
